<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Hans Starck und Peter Beheym,
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> amptman des Hemerlein czu Burkheim
              <add>gesellen</add> dem Sweyker von Salach, <add>des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
              Starken armman</add>, funff pferd und <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Perynger, des
            Peter Beheims <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, sechs pferd genomen und
                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Perynger darczu gefangen und gen Burkhaim gefürt
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ewrm amptman
            schicken und bestellen wöllet, daz der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger <expan>armenlewte<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ire pferde wider und auch der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">C.</expan>
<expan>Pering<ex>er</ex></expan> ledig werde. Als etc. Das
              <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii post Mathey <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
